                    <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink/70"></span>
                    Clear communication and on-time arrivals.
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink/70"></span>
                    Clean, detailed work that makes the yard feel cared for.
                  </li>
